data.description: Absolutely stunning home in Lake Forest! Enter this grand opening foyer with 12' Ceilings. This beautiful 5 bed / 4 bath luxury home features an open floorplan w/wood flooring in the all areas of the first floor! Gourmet kitchen w/large center island, granite counter tops, gas cook top, and breakfast area, separate formal dining, master suite is very spacious w/sitting area,  state of the art surround sound on the 1st floor.  Bonus room gives  additional entertainment space / office. Enjoy a prestigious walk to the lake and enjoy a relaxing evening as you stroll looking over the water a community of Lake Forest. Close to shopping & eating in Madison Town Center, RSA Gate 7,  & Research Park.
